Suggestions

1.Reduce tariffs and taxes for the crops that are coming from South America.
2. Make Trade agreements with Avocado growers from South America to ensure steady supply .
3. During the months of low sales host food shows in grocery stores to attract more customers.
4.  Advertise more all year around will help boost the sales.
